metadata.name: Seize the HODL
metadata.description:
This one-of-a-kind, digital collectible features an ASCII art of Pepe the frog, with a determined expression and the famous HODL acronym written across its chest. The ASCII art Pepe is a unique representation of the meme that has become synonymous with internet culture. Not only is this meme guaranteed to make you laugh, but it's also a symbol of the crypto community's unwavering faith in the long-term value of their investments. This NFT is the perfect addition to any crypto enthusiast's collection, and a must-have for anyone who loves memes and the power of HODLing. Don't miss out on this limited edition, digital masterpiece - get your hands on "Seize the HODL" now!

The owners of this NFT will be the first users of HODLbooster. They will be able to reclaim all of the money by burning this NFT after waiting for HODLbooster to make a profit for them in the following years.
